platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 世界中を旅して花を咲かせよう
化身花瓣 隨風飄舞

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Is Flower a puzzle game or is it a meditative adventure in which the sheer spectacle of floating across its stunning landscapes absorbs all your attention? Yes. Traditional gameplay concepts are paired with novel interactions, and masterful use of color, sound, and movement. Flower is as much an artful expression of rebirth and regeneration as it is a game, and an experience that broadens the understanding of what a game can be.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: 化為一片花瓣，隨風飄零，飛過白天黑夜，在美景中感受大自然的禪意。
成為一片花瓣，飛過白晝、黃昏與黑夜，感受源於大自然的禪意。
Évadez-vous avec une expérience interactive inédite et poétique.
